long_description: Suffering from heel pain can be a bummer. Find relief with these performance gel heel cups that also will enhance the fit of your footwear. Dual density thermo polyurethane rubber gel combines superior cushioning and energy return for enhance performance. Dual density gels absorb impact and shock where your heels need it most and also promotes a natural walking motion. Slip-resistant design ensures that the heel cups stay in place. Cupped heels provide extra cushioning and stability for your heels. Provides temporary pain relief from heel conditions like plantar fasciitis.
